title: Commission responds to detention changes on Nauru (Australian Human Rights Commission)
text: ( Source : Australian Human Rights Commission ) The Australian Human Rights Commission today repeats its call for the Federal Government to end the detention of asylum seekers on Nauru and for them to be returned to Australia for processing.
